George, you got jury duty!

01:05.587 --> 01:08.111
GEORGE SR.:
Tell 'em I died!

01:08.155 --> 01:09.808
ADULT SHELDON:
And one time...

01:09.852 --> 01:12.202
Missy, you got something.

01:12.246 --> 01:15.031
...mail caused a war
between neighbors

01:15.075 --> 01:17.425
rivaling that
of the Klingon Empire

01:17.468 --> 01:20.732
