trust me-- was a doozy.

01:20.776 --> 01:22.082
What'd you get?

01:22.125 --> 01:24.214
An invitation
to Billy's birthday party.

01:24.258 --> 01:25.955
That's nice.

01:25.998 --> 01:28.566
