01:40.709 --> 01:42.232
It didn't get lost.

01:42.276 --> 01:44.016
What are you saying?

01:44.060 --> 01:46.454
I think you know
what I'm saying.

01:46.497 --> 01:49.021
So Sheldon isn't invited?

01:49.065 --> 01:50.458
See? You knew. Bye.

