All right, Moon Pie.
I'll see you after class.

02:14.221 --> 02:15.700
Aren't you going
to walk me in?

02:15.744 --> 02:17.224
I think you can manage it.

02:17.267 --> 02:19.226
Is it because you're trying
to avoid Dr. Sturgis?

02:19.269 --> 02:21.141
No.
Is it because
you're getting old,

02:21.184 --> 02:24.187
and you're trying to limit
the number of steps you take?Get in there.

02:24.231 --> 02:25.362
Connie.

02:25.406 --> 02:28.148
Oh, hello, John.

02:28.191 --> 02:29.584
It's nice to see you.

02:29.627 --> 02:31.803
It's nice to see you, too.I assumed

02:31.847 --> 02:33.805
you stopped bringing
Sheldon to class

02:33.849 --> 02:36.591
