04:09.901 --> 04:12.295
Thank you so much, Sheldon.
I think we got this.

04:12.339 --> 04:17.082
Yes. Well, uh, Sheldon, uh,
s-see you next week.

04:17.126 --> 04:20.738
Bye. Can you explain why you
didn't settle on a specific date

04:20.782 --> 04:23.175
for coffee with
Dr. Sturgis?

04:23.219 --> 04:25.874
Maybe another time.
