with Sheldon.

04:30.922 --> 04:32.576
That boy's only other friend
is a chicken

04:32.620 --> 04:34.230
and she's worried about Sheldon?

04:34.274 --> 04:37.320
What do we do?
Tell Missy she can't go?

04:37.364 --> 04:38.843
If we're only gonna
let Missy go places

04:38.887 --> 04:40.062
where they want
to have Sheldon,

04:40.105 --> 04:41.542
then she ain't gonna
get out much.

04:41.585 --> 04:43.413
Well, I don't think
it's right that...

04:45.459 --> 04:47.374
Sup.

