your father and I are talking?

04:51.160 --> 04:53.336
Yeah, but you can
talk anywhere,

04:53.380 --> 04:56.557
and this is the only room
in the house with a TV.

04:56.600 --> 04:58.123
Get out of here.

04:58.167 --> 05:00.517
Suit yourself.

05:00.561 --> 05:02.302
But I'd like to point out,

05:02.345 --> 05:04.304
if you'd let me buy a TV
for my bedroom,

05:04.347 --> 05:06.349
we wouldn't be in this
situation, now would we?

05:06.393 --> 05:08.830
Go.

05:08.873 --> 05:10.614
I just hate

05:10.658 --> 05:12.529
that our little boy
gets left out.

05:12.573 --> 05:15.358
Me, too, but he should
probably get used to it.

05:15.402 --> 05:17.752
That's a terrible thing to say.

05:17.795 --> 05:21.321
Oh, come on, Mary, the boy's
not exactly a social butterfly.

05:21.364 --> 05:23.758
In fact, he's scared
of butterflies.

05:23.801 --> 05:25.020
Besides,
it's their house.

05:25.063 --> 05:26.369
If they don't want him,

05:26.413 --> 05:27.979
there's nothing
you can do about it.

05:30.025 --> 05:33.594
Pastor Jeff, are you
still looking for a topic

05:33.637 --> 05:35.030
