05:35.073 --> 05:36.858
You mean the one I'm
doing in 20 minutes?

05:36.901 --> 05:39.991
Sorry, silly question.No.

05:40.035 --> 05:42.080
What do you got?
I was gonna do Noah's ark,

05:42.124 --> 05:44.300
but Sheldon's
gonna eat me alive,

05:44.344 --> 05:46.781
like those two lions would've
done to those two giraffes.

05:46.824 --> 05:50.306
Well, I've been thinking
about the importance

05:50.350 --> 05:52.352
of being neighborly.

05:54.441 --> 05:56.443
CONGREGATION:
♪ Heart of my

