06:25.559 --> 06:28.170
Sheldon,
it's a rhetorical question.

06:28.213 --> 06:30.433
Aw.
He said it was

06:30.477 --> 06:34.698
to love God and love
your neighbor as yourself.

06:34.742 --> 06:37.048
