to talk about today,

06:37.092 --> 06:40.269
being a good neighbor.
How do we love our neighbors?

06:40.312 --> 06:42.402
We check in on them,

06:42.445 --> 06:44.447
we welcome them
into our homes.

06:44.491 --> 06:46.667
If we're having a party,
we invite them.

06:46.710 --> 06:48.538
Even if they're not
the most popular.Are you kidding me?

06:48.582 --> 06:49.931
Shh.

06:49.974 --> 06:51.889
Some of the Romans
thought he was a little weird,

06:51.933 --> 06:54.457
but if you invite him
into your heart,

06:54.501 --> 06:57.547
you get to go to
the biggest party of all,

06:57.591 --> 06:59.157
the one in the sky.

06:59.201 --> 07:01.290
Ooh, a party
in the sky.

07:01.333 --> 07:03.379
Fun.
He means heaven.

07:03.423 --> 07:05.337
