07:05.381 --> 07:07.427
He means heaven.

07:07.470 --> 07:11.039
I can't believe you told
on me to Pastor Jeff.

07:11.082 --> 07:13.476
I have no idea what
you're talking about.

07:13.520 --> 07:15.260
Hi, neighbor.

07:15.304 --> 07:16.479
Hi.JEFF: No matter
how funny they look.

07:20.396 --> 07:21.615
It just don't
make no sense.

07:21.658 --> 07:23.443
If I'm gonna pay for it
with my own money,

07:23.486 --> 07:25.270
why can't I get a TV
for my bedroom?

07:25.314 --> 07:27.403
You have so much money, why
don't you save it for college?

07:27.447 --> 07:28.883
If you're not gonna
take this seriously,

07:28.926 --> 07:30.711
I don't even know why
I'm talking to you.

07:30.754 --> 07:32.713
Your mother won't let me
have a TV in my room,

07:32.756 --> 07:34.279
so you're not
getting one in yours.

07:34.323 --> 07:37.239
Why do you care what Mom says?

07:37.282 --> 07:39.502
You're the man of the house,
what you say goes.

07:39.546 --> 07:41.199
If you're not gonna
take this seriously,

07:41.243 --> 07:42.723
I don't know why
