08:08.662 --> 08:12.404
Well, that's true.Well, bar it is.

08:12.448 --> 08:14.406
How's, uh, 2:00?

08:14.450 --> 08:19.324
Uh, today's not great for me.
Uh, maybe some other time.

08:20.674 --> 08:22.458
Oh, I understand.

08:22.502 --> 08:25.853
Uh, I won't bother you again.

08:25.896 --> 08:28.899
Well, it's not like that,
y-you know,

08:28.943 --> 08:30.684
I'm just kind of busy right now.

08:30.727 --> 08:34.209
Of course, you made that
perfectly clear.

08:34.252 --> 08:36.646
Goodbye.

08:39.344 --> 08:42.130
You just dump
somebody?
No.

08:42.173 --> 08:45.525
Dr. Sturgis wanted to hang out,

08:45.568 --> 08:46.874
and I'm busy.

08:46.917 --> 08:49.659
Yeah, busy breaking hearts.

08:57.928 --> 09:00.452
You win. Hope
you're happy.

09:02.280 --> 09:05.022
This was never
about winners and losers.

09:05.066 --> 09:07.547
Two kids means two gifts.

09:07.590 --> 09:11.115
