he'll just eat it.

09:16.643 --> 09:19.602
Hey, Shelly,
I got something for you.

09:19.646 --> 09:20.603
What is it?

09:20.647 --> 09:22.518
An invitation
to Billy Sparks's

09:22.562 --> 09:25.216
birthday on Saturday.
Isn't that nice?

09:25.260 --> 09:26.783
Sheldon's gonna go?

09:26.827 --> 09:29.569
