adult no one wants to be around.

10:28.453 --> 10:30.325
Damn it.

10:31.718 --> 10:33.502
Oh.

10:33.545 --> 10:34.764
Hello.

10:34.808 --> 10:36.287
Hey, John.

10:36.331 --> 10:38.159
Oh, George.

10:38.202 --> 10:40.596
Uh, you just caught me
on my way out...

10:40.640 --> 10:42.642
to a party... with people.

10:42.685 --> 10:44.600
A people party.

10:44.644 --> 10:47.516
Sure. Hey, listen,
I just wanted to let you know

10:47.559 --> 10:50.693
