and watch a game.

10:52.913 --> 10:57.439
I don't know
if Saturday works for me. Uh...

10:57.482 --> 10:59.267
Okay, well,
you just let me know.

10:59.310 --> 11:00.616
Wait!

11:00.660 --> 11:03.532
Saturday's fine. I'll be there.

11:03.575 --> 11:04.968
Okay.

11:05.012 --> 11:06.666
Have a good night.

11:06.709 --> 11:08.580
Goodbye!

11:09.625 --> 11:11.627
Sheldon's going
to that party.

11:11.671 --> 11:13.890
I'm a good liar.

11:15.979 --> 11:17.981
What'd I get him?

11:18.025 --> 11:19.200
Connect Four.

11:19.243 --> 11:21.637
That was thoughtful of me.Shelly?

11:21.681 --> 11:23.117
Come on!
It's time to go.

11:23.160 --> 11:24.727
Do I have to
wait for Sheldon?

11:24.771 --> 11:26.294
Can't I just go now?

11:26.337 --> 11:28.252
No, we're going together
as a family.

11:29.689 --> 11:30.777
Greetings, Mother.

11:30.820 --> 11:32.996
I'm ready to beam down
to the party.

11:35.042 --> 11:36.347
You go on ahead.

11:36.391 --> 11:38.436
Oh, thank you, Jesus.

11:39.481 --> 11:41.483
What do you think
you are wearing?

11:41.526 --> 11:42.832
A Mr. Spock outfit.

11:42.876 --> 11:44.704
I know it's a
Mr. Spock outfit.

